INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('1', '科技爱好者周刊（第 285 期）：为什么 PPT 不如备忘录', '1', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">日期： 2024年1月 5日</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">这里记录每周值得分享的科技内容，周五发布。</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.beekka.com/blogimg/asset/202401/bg2024010316.webp\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 213); font-size: 16px;\">西安某小区正在新建的儿童游乐园。（</span><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/C0iKVDtry1c/?img_index=6\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-align: left;\">via</a><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 213); font-size: 16px;\">）</span></p>', '<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">为什么 PPT 不如备忘录</h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\">莱克斯·弗里德曼（Lex Fridman）是一个非常有名的美国主持人，他的播客节目影响很大，很多名人都愿意上他的节目，接受专访。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.beekka.com/blogimg/asset/202312/bg2023122209.webp\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">12月15日的节目嘉宾，是亚马逊公司的创始人贝佐斯。他们一共谈了两个多小时。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.beekka.com/blogimg/asset/202312/bg2023122210.webp\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">贝佐斯已经不担任亚马逊 CEO，只留任董事会，算是半退休了，主要精力都放在他的太空旅游公司\"蓝色起源\"（Blue Origin）。从现场照片看，他退休后显得更年轻健壮，精力旺盛。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">这个采访有很多有意思的内容，YouTube 有<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DcWqzZ3I2cY\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-align: left;\">完整的视频</a>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">我想分享其中一段，贝佐斯谈<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?ref=saved&amp;v=1007951996967519\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-align: left;\">亚马逊是怎么开会的</a>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">主持人问贝佐斯：\"我听说<strong>亚马逊开会时，不准使用 PPT，发言人必须提交一份六页的备忘录</strong>。这是真的吗？\"</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">这个事情一直是传闻，但这一次，贝佐斯亲口承认确实如此。\"新来的人可能会大吃一惊，我们的开会方式与众不同。\"</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">\"会议的前30分钟，我们是不说话的。大家在会议室中安静地坐在一起，阅读这份六页的备忘录，在空白处做笔记，过了30分钟才开始讨论。\"</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">这真的很奇怪，你见过半个小时没人说话的会议吗？</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">贝佐斯解释：\"你可以说，更好的做法是，大家都提前阅读这些备忘录。但问题是，人们没有时间这样做，他们参加会议只是因为必须出席。\"</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">\"我们索性在会议上留出时间，让大家现场阅读材料，然后就可以进行真正高层次的讨论了，所有人都跟得上讨论的主题，不会搞不清一些基本的事实。\"</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">那么，为什么一定要当事人提交六页的备忘录，而不是现场主讲 PPT 呢？</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">贝佐斯说，<strong>书面的备忘录要比 PPT 演示，效果好得多</strong>，主要有以下几点原因。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">（1）PPT 的设计目的是说服，这是一种销售工具。但是在公司内部，你想要的是真相，而不是业务主管的推销。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">（2）PPT 的缺点是，它对作者相对容易，对观众来说却很难抓住要点。备忘录正好相反，写好一份六页的备忘录，对于作者是很难的。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">你可能需要两周的时间，先写出初稿，然后再重写，不断加工，确保你的文字是准确和可靠的。所以，备忘录对作者非常困难，但对观众就好多了，半小时的阅读就能搞清楚事情的来龙去脉，也看得出作者对这个问题的熟悉程度。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">（3）备忘录可以节省会议时间。如果是 PPT 演示，高管们会不停地打断提问，结果发现答案就在下一张幻灯片。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">但是，阅读备忘录时，你必须先把所有问题写在空白处，当你读到最后一页时，发现很多问题已经得到了解答，这就节省了当众提问的时间。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">（4）PPT 演示过程中，主讲人也许会根据现场情况，临时决定隐藏或修改一些讲法。备忘录就没有这个问题，主讲人必须事先给出完整描述，你更能了解他的真实想法。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">（5）PPT 通常只是一些要点，不是完整的句子，有利于隐藏很多草率的想法。而备忘录是完整的段落，必须有主题句，有动词和名词，你很难隐藏自己的草率思维。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">备忘录迫使作者处于最佳状态，你能得到一个人真正最好的想法。如果 PPT 演示，你们可能要讨论很久，发言人才能进入最佳状态。从长远来看，备忘录节省了你的时间。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">以上就是贝佐斯不允许使用 PPT 的五点理由。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">我觉得这些理由很有说服力。PPT 在国内已经泛滥成灾，大家好像默认，它是开会的标准方式，缺了还不行。这真的要改一下，学习亚马逊的\"备忘录开会法\"----<strong>先写成文档，再进行讨论</strong>----可能是更好更正确的做法。</p>', '0', '1362', '1', '2024-01-15 19:37:19', '2024-01-15 19:37:19');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('2', '每日一题', '2', '<p><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/LeetCode.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p>', '<p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">太久不写算法真的要荒废了<span style=\"color: transparent; background-color: rgb(216, 238, 250);\">或许已经没有什么可荒废的了?</span>，立个 flag，每天至少写一题吧...以 Google 爬虫为证...就用 Java 写吧，还记得当时面试时的尴尬，因为写了几个月 cpp，Java 的库函数都调不出来...</p><h1>2021.12</h1><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/battleships-in-a-board/\" target=\"_blank\">419. 甲板上的战舰</a> - 21.12.18</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    int[] dx = {0,1,0,-1};\n    int[] dy = {1,0,-1,0};\n    int m;\n    int n;\n\n    public int countBattleships(char[][] board) {\n        m = board.length;\n        n = board[0].length;\n        int ans = 0;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; m;i++){\n            for(int j = 0;j &lt; n;j++){\n                if(board[i][j] == \'X\'){\n                    dfs(board,i,j);\n                    ans++;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n    public void dfs(char[][] board, int x, int y){\n        board[x][y] = \'.\';\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; 4;i++){\n            int nx = x + dx[i];\n            int ny = y + dy[i];\n            if(judge(nx,ny) &amp;&amp; board[nx][ny] == \'X\'){\n                dfs(board,nx,ny);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    public boolean judge(int x,int y){\n        if(x &lt; 0 || y &lt; 0 || x &gt;= m || y &gt;= n)return false;\n        return true;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211218235803836.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211218235803836.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">第一眼的想法也就是 DFS 了，至于进阶中的要求，和题目的关联比较大，看了下官方题解，也没必要重新再写了</p><blockquote>进阶： 你可以实现一次扫描算法，并只使用 O(1) 额外空间，并且不修改 board 的值来解决这个问题吗？</blockquote><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/find-the-town-judge\" target=\"_blank\">997. 找到小镇的法官</a> - 21.12.19</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int findJudge(int n, int[][] trust) {\n        int[] trustIdNum = new int[n+1];\n        for(int[] t : trust){\n            trustIdNum[t[1]]++;\n            trustIdNum[t[0]]--;\n        }\n        for(int i = 1;i &lt;= n;i++){\n            if(trustIdNum[i] == n - 1) return i;\n        }\n        return -1;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211219010206467.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211219010206467.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">一开始用 map 和 set 来做的，发现耗时和内存太高了，看了下别人的题解，确实杀鸡用牛刀了。根据题目描述，小镇上所有人都信任法官，而法官不信任任何人，所以只要保证信任法官的人数==小镇人数-1，简单的一道题。</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211219010708459.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211219010708459.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">评论区都是人才，超喜欢的。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/heaters\" target=\"_blank\">475. 供暖器</a> - 21.12.20</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int findRadius(int[] houses, int[] heaters) {\n        Arrays.sort(houses);\n        Arrays.sort(heaters);\n        //存放每个房屋离最近加热器的距离\n        int[] distance = new int[houses.length];\n        int p1 = 0;\n        int p2 = heaters.length - 1;\n        \n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; houses.length;i++){\n            //从前往后找房屋左边最近的一个供暖器\n            while(p1 &lt; heaters.length -1 &amp;&amp; houses[i] &gt; heaters[p1]) p1++;\n            distance[i] = Math.abs(heaters[p1] - houses[i]);\n        }\n\n        for(int i = houses.length - 1; i &gt;= 0;i--){\n            //从后往前找房屋右边最近的一个供暖器\n            while(p2 &gt;= 1 &amp;&amp; houses[i] &lt; heaters[p2]) p2--;\n            //和第一遍遍历得到的最近距离比较，留下更近的那个\n            distance[i] = Math.min(distance[i],Math.abs(heaters[p2] - houses[i]));\n        }\n\n        int ans = 0;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; houses.length;i++){\n            //所有距离中最远的那个就是最小的半径\n            ans = Math.max(ans,distance[i]);\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211220233715003.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211220233715003.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">没什么思路，看了下官方题解日常写天书，评论区找到个讲人话的思路挺对味</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">调生物钟难受得一批，直接睡觉</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/day-of-the-year\" target=\"_blank\">1154. 一年中的第几天</a> - 21.12.21</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-javascript\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int dayOfYear(String date) {\n        return java.time.LocalDate.parse(date).getDayOfYear();\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211221134324113.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211221134324113.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">感觉这种问题当个 API 战士才是合理的，但既然是算法，还是写一下吧...</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int dayOfYear(String date) {\n        int[] day4month = {31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};\n        int year = (date.charAt(0) - \'0\') * 1000 + \n                    (date.charAt(1) - \'0\') * 100 +\n                    (date.charAt(2) - \'0\') * 10 +\n                    date.charAt(3) - \'0\';\n        int month = (date.charAt(5) - \'0\') * 10 + date.charAt(6) - \'0\';\n        int day = (date.charAt(8) - \'0\') * 10 + date.charAt(9) - \'0\';\n        int ans = day;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; month - 1;i++) ans += day4month[i];\n        if(((year % 4 == 0 &amp;&amp; year % 100 != 0) || year % 400 == 0) &amp;&amp; month &gt; 2)ans++;\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211221143336912.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211221143336912.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/intersection-of-two-linked-lists\" target=\"_blank\">160. 相交链表</a></h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">随机一题写一写</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">public class Solution {\n    public ListNode getIntersectionNode(ListNode headA, ListNode headB) {\n        if(headA == null || headB == null) return null;\n        ListNode p1 = headA;\n        ListNode p2 = headB;\n        while(p1 != p2){\n            //走到尾部后，转向另一个链表头部\n            p1 = p1 == null ? headB : p1.next;\n            p2 = p2 == null ? headA : p2.next;\n        }\n        //两个指针相等时，跳出循环，此时要么指向相交节点，要么不相交指向null\n        return p1;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211221223524821.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211221223524821.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">题解普遍有两种方法，第一种用 HashSet，把其中一条链表全部存进 Set 里，遍历第二条链表时判断是否存在。</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">第二种用双指针，算脑筋急转弯了，两个指针分别从两条链表头前进，当其中一个指针到达尾部 null 时，就指向另一条链表头，当两个指针都交换过链表后，一直前进，总会遇到那个相同的节点（null 也视为相同节点），如此只需返回两个指针相同时的那个节点便可（为 null 则为不相交，否则便是相交）。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/repeated-string-match\" target=\"_blank\">686. 重复叠加字符串匹配</a> - 21.12.22</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int repeatedStringMatch(String a, String b) {\n        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();\n        int ans = 0;\n        while(sb.length() &lt; b.length()){\n            ans++;\n            sb.append(a);\n        }\n        //如果存在答案，只需保证a的长度大于b即可，所以再拼接一次\n        sb.append(a);\n        int index = strStr(sb.toString(),b);\n        if(index == -1) return -1;\n        return index + b.length() &lt;= a.length() * ans ? ans : ans + 1;\n    }\n\n    public int strStr(String haystack, String needle) {\n        int lenS = haystack.length();\n        int lenP = needle.length();\n        char[] s = haystack.toCharArray();\n        char[] p = needle.toCharArray();\n\n        int[] next = new int[lenP + 1];\n        next[0] = -1;\n        for(int i = 0, tmp = -1; i &lt; lenP; ){\n            if(tmp == -1 || p[i] == p[tmp]) next[++i] = ++tmp;\n            else tmp = next[tmp];\n        }\n\n        int i = 0, j = 0;\n        while(i &lt; lenS &amp;&amp; j &lt; lenP){\n            if(j == -1 || s[i] == p[j]){\n                i++;\n                j++;\n            }else{\n                j = next[j];\n            }\n        }\n        if(j == lenP) return i - j;\n        return -1;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211222210323556.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211222210323556.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">这题有个理论，即明确复制次数的「上界」和「下界」，参考<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/repeated-string-match/solution/gong-shui-san-xie-yi-ti-san-jie-qia-chan-3hbr/\" target=\"_blank\">【宫水三叶】的题解</a>。而这种「模式串 pattern」不变的子串匹配可以沿用 <a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/implement-strstr\" target=\"_blank\">LeetCode - 28. 实现 strStr()</a> 中使用的 KMP 算法。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/implement-strstr\" target=\"_blank\">28. 实现 strStr()</a></h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int strStr(String haystack, String needle) {\n        int lenS = haystack.length();\n        int lenP = needle.length();\n        char[] s = haystack.toCharArray();\n        char[] p = needle.toCharArray();\n\n        int[] next = new int[lenP + 1];\n        next[0] = -1;\n        for(int i = 0, tmp = -1; i &lt; lenP; ){\n            if(tmp == -1 || p[i] == p[tmp]) next[++i] = ++tmp;\n            else tmp = next[tmp];\n        }\n\n        int i = 0, j = 0;\n        while(i &lt; lenS &amp;&amp; j &lt; lenP){\n            if(j == -1 || s[i] == p[j]){\n                i++;\n                j++;\n            }else{\n                j = next[j];\n            }\n        }\n        if(j == lenP) return i - j;\n        return -1;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211222194704996.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211222194704996.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">过于抽象的算法，当场推 next 数组太费脑细胞了，当成算法模板用得了。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/longest-duplicate-substring\" target=\"_blank\">1044. 最长重复子串</a> - 21.12.23</h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    long[] h,p;\n    public String longestDupSubstring(String s) {\n        int P = 31, n = s.length();\n        h = new long[n + 10];\n        p = new long[n + 10];\n        p[0] = 1;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; n;i++){\n            p[i+1] = p[i] * P;\n            h[i+1] = h[i] * P + s.charAt(i);\n        }\n        String ans = \"\";\n        int l = 0, r = n;\n        while(l &lt; r){\n            int mid = l + r + 1 &gt;&gt; 1;\n            String t = check(s,mid);\n            if(t.length() != 0) l = mid;\n            else r = mid - 1;\n            ans = t.length() &gt; ans.length() ? t : ans;\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n    public String check(String s, int len){\n        int n = s.length();\n        Set&lt;Long&gt; set = new HashSet&lt;&gt;();\n        for(int i = 1; i + len - 1 &lt;= n;i++){\n            int j = i + len - 1;\n            long cur = h[j] - h[i - 1] * p[j - i + 1];\n            if(set.contains(cur)) return s.substring(i - 1,j);\n            set.add(cur);\n        }\n        return \"\";\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211223213403230.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211223213403230.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">实在太难了，下辈子都写不出来。直接冲去看题解，说是周赛原题，国服只有 6 个人做出来。被迫学习一下新知识，<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/longest-duplicate-substring/solution/gong-shui-san-xie-zi-fu-chuan-ha-xi-ying-hae9/\" target=\"_blank\">「字符串哈希 + 二分」</a>。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/maximum-number-of-eaten-apples\" target=\"_blank\">1705. 吃苹果的最大数目</a> - 21.12.24</h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int eatenApples(int[] apples, int[] days) {\n        int ans = 0;\n        int n = apples.length;\n        // int[]={苹果数量，在哪天过期}\n        PriorityQueue&lt;int[]&gt; heap = new PriorityQueue&lt;&gt;((a1,a2) -&gt; a1[1] - a2[1]);\n\n        //当前的天数\n        int d = 0;\n        while(d &lt; n || !heap.isEmpty()){\n            if(d &lt; n &amp;&amp; apples[d] &gt; 0){\n                heap.offer(new int[]{apples[d], d + days[d]});\n            }\n            //吃队首的苹果\n            if(!heap.isEmpty()){\n                int[] head = heap.peek();\n                head[0]--;\n                ans++;\n                if(head[0] == 0){\n                    //没有苹果了，就移除这个节点\n                    heap.poll();\n                }\n            }\n            //每天天数都要+1，即使超过n天\n            d++;\n            //移除过期的苹果\n            while(!heap.isEmpty() &amp;&amp; heap.peek()[1] &lt;= d){\n                heap.poll();\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211224234910891.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211224234910891.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">维护一个优先级队列来存放「苹果数量，在哪天过期」，按照贪心策略，吃最早过期的即是吃队首的苹果，便能够保证吃的最多。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/even-odd-tree\" target=\"_blank\">1609. 奇偶树</a> - 21.12.25</h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public boolean isEvenOddTree(TreeNode root) {\n        Queue&lt;TreeNode&gt; q = new LinkedList&lt;&gt;();\n        q.offer(root);\n        //偶数层\n        boolean evenLevel = true;\n        while(!q.isEmpty()){\n            //该层节点个数\n            int size = q.size();\n            //前一个节点的值，偶数层需要递增，奇数层需要递减\n            int prev = evenLevel ? -1 : 0x7fffffff;\n            while(size-- &gt; 0){\n                TreeNode node = q.poll();\n                if(evenLevel &amp;&amp; (node.val % 2 == 0 || node.val &lt;= prev)) return false;\n                if(!evenLevel &amp;&amp; (node.val % 2 != 0 || node.val &gt;= prev)) return false;\n                prev = node.val;\n                if(node.left != null) q.offer(node.left);\n                if(node.right != null) q.offer(node.right);\n            }\n            evenLevel = !evenLevel;\n        }\n        return true;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211225214902494.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211225214902494.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">简单 BFS 一下</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/occurrences-after-bigram\" target=\"_blank\">1078. Bigram 分词</a> - 21.12.26</h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public String[] findOcurrences(String text, String first, String second) {\n        String[] split = text.split(\" \");\n        List&lt;String&gt; ans = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\n        for(int i = 0;i + 2&lt; split.length;i++){\n            if(split[i].equals(first) &amp;&amp; split[i+1].equals(second)){\n                ans.add(split[i + 2]);\n            }\n        }\n        return ans.toArray(new String[0]);\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211226144126151.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211226144126151.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">有趣的是，如果<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>split</code></span>中使用正则<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>\\\\s+</code></span>来匹配空格的话，耗时会增加到 3ms，掉到 10%，没想到差别这么大</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/friends-of-appropriate-ages\" target=\"_blank\">825. 适龄的朋友</a> - 21.12.27</h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int numFriendRequests(int[] ages) {\n        Arrays.sort(ages);\n        int n = ages.length;\n        int ans = 0;\n        for(int i = 0, l = 0, r = 0;i &lt; n;i++){\n            while(l &lt; i &amp;&amp; !judge(ages[l],ages[i])) l++;\n            if(r &lt; i) r = i;\n            while(r &lt; n &amp;&amp; judge(ages[r],ages[i])) r++;\n            ans += Math.max(0,r - l - 1);\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n    public boolean judge(int x,int y){\n        if(y &lt;= 0.5 * x + 7) return false;\n        if(y &gt; x) return false;\n        return true;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211227234053363.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211227234053363.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">这题的题目描述莫名其妙的，还有多余的条件</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">用「排序+双指针」的做法，需要根据条件推导出规律，符合条件的在一条连续段上</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/concatenated-words\" target=\"_blank\">472. 连接词</a> - 21.12.28</h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    private Node root = new Node();\n    \n    public List&lt;String&gt; findAllConcatenatedWordsInADict(String[] words) {\n        List&lt;String&gt; ans = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\n        Arrays.sort(words,(a,b) -&gt; a.length() - b.length());\n        for(String word : words){\n            if (!word.isEmpty()) {\n                if (dfs(word, 0)) {\n                    ans.add(word);\n                } else {\n                    insert(word);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n    private boolean dfs(String word, int i) {\n        if (i == word.length()) {\n            return true;\n        }\n        Node node = this.root;\n        while (i &lt; word.length()) {\n            if (node.children[word.charAt(i) - \'a\'] == null) {\n                return false;\n            }\n            node = node.children[word.charAt(i) - \'a\'];\n            if (node.isEnd &amp;&amp; dfs(word, i + 1)) {\n                return true;\n            }\n            i++;\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n\n    private void insert(String word) {\n        Node node = this.root;\n        for (int i = 0; i &lt; word.length(); i++) {\n            if (node.children[word.charAt(i) - \'a\'] == null) {\n                node.children[word.charAt(i) - \'a\'] = new Node();\n            }\n            node = node.children[word.charAt(i) - \'a\'];\n        }\n        node.isEnd = true;\n    }\n\n    class Node {\n        boolean isEnd;\n        Node[] children;\n        Node() {\n            this.isEnd = false;\n            this.children = new Node[26];\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211228235641330.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211228235641330.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">学习一下「<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/concatenated-words/solution/tong-ge-lai-shua-ti-la-zi-dian-shu-dfs-b-dk9c/\" target=\"_blank\">字典树 &amp; DFS</a>」</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/count-special-quadruplets\" target=\"_blank\">1995. 统计特殊四元组</a> - 21.12.29</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int countQuadruplets(int[] nums) {\n        int n = nums.length;\n        int ans = 0;\n        for(int a = 0; a &lt; n;a++){\n            for(int b = a + 1; b &lt; n;b++){\n                for(int c = b + 1; c &lt; n; c++){\n                    for(int d = c + 1; d &lt; n; d++){\n                        if(nums[a] + nums[b] + nums[c] == nums[d]){\n                            ans++;\n                        }\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211229232748722.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211229232748722.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">对于这个数据量的题，暴力也不失为一种优雅的做法</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/hand-of-straights\" target=\"_blank\">846. 一手顺子</a> - 21.12.30</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public boolean isNStraightHand(int[] hand, int groupSize) {\n        int n = hand.length;\n        if(n % groupSize != 0) return false;\n\n        Map&lt;Integer,Integer&gt; map = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n        Queue&lt;Integer&gt; heap = new PriorityQueue&lt;&gt;();\n        for(int i : hand){\n            map.merge(i, 1, Integer::sum);\n            heap.add(i);\n        }\n        while(!heap.isEmpty()){\n            int num = heap.poll();\n            if(map.get(num) == 0) continue;\n            for(int i = 0;i &lt; groupSize;i++){\n                int cnt = map.getOrDefault(num + i, 0);\n                if(cnt == 0) return false;\n                map.merge(num + i, -1, Integer::sum);\n            }\n        }\n        return true;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211230235743803.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211230235743803.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">又 Get 到了一种优先队列（小根堆）的用法</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/perfect-number\" target=\"_blank\">507. 完美数</a> - 21.12.31</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public boolean checkPerfectNumber(int num) {\n        if(num == 1) return false;\n        int sum = 1;\n        for(int i = 2;i * i &lt; num;i++){\n            if(num % i == 0){\n                sum += i;\n                sum += num / i;\n            }\n        }\n        return sum == num;\n        //return num == 6 || num == 28 || num == 496 || num == 8128 || num == 33550336;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20211231214847180.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20211231214847180.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h1>2022.01</h1><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/convert-1d-array-into-2d-array\" target=\"_blank\">2022. 将一维数组转变成二维数组</a> - 22.01.01</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">三种方法</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>遍历赋值</code></span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-javascript\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int[][] construct2DArray(int[] original, int m, int n) {\n        int len = original.length;\n        if(len != m * n) return new int[0][0];\n        int[][] ans = new int[m][n];\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; len;i++){\n            ans[i / n][i % n] = original[i];\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220101151356127.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220101151356127.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>Arrays.copyOfRange</code></span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int[][] construct2DArray(int[] original, int m, int n) {\n        int len = original.length;\n        if(len != m * n) return new int[0][0];\n        int[][] ans = new int[m][];\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; m;i++){\n            ans[i] = Arrays.copyOfRange(original,i * n,(i + 1) * n);\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220101154111350.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220101154111350.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>System.arraycopy</code></span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int[][] construct2DArray(int[] original, int m, int n) {\n        int len = original.length;\n        if(len != m * n) return new int[0][0];\n        int[][] ans = new int[m][n];\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; m;i++){\n            System.arraycopy(original,i * n,ans[i],0,n);\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220101154815889.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220101154815889.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">这些提交结果没什么参考价值，<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>Arrays.copyOfRange</code></span>实际上也是调用的<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>System.arraycopy</code></span>的<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>native</code></span>方法</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/elimination-game\" target=\"_blank\">390. 消除游戏</a> - 22.01.02</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int lastRemaining(int n) {\n        int head = 1;\n        int step = 1;\n        boolean isLeft = true;\n        while(n &gt; 1){\n            //从左到右删除，因为列表第一个会被删除，所以head总会向下一个位置移动\n            //从右到左删除\n            //    如果列表是奇数个，则第一个位置会被删除，head会向下一个位置移动\n            //    如果列表是偶数个，则第一个位置不会被删除，head无需移动\n            if(isLeft || n % 2 != 0){\n                head += step;\n            }\n            step *= 2;\n            n /= 2;\n            isLeft = !isLeft;\n        }\n        return head;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220102233949615.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220102233949615.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">斐波那契变体，直接用模拟做</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/day-of-the-week\" target=\"_blank\">1185. 一周中的第几天</a> - 22.01.03</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public String dayOfTheWeek(int day, int month, int year) {\n        String[] week = {\"Sunday\", \"Monday\", \"Tuesday\", \"Wednesday\", \"Thursday\", \"Friday\", \"Saturday\"};\n        //1970最后一天是星期四\n        int ans = 4 + day;\n        for(int i = 1971;i &lt; year;i++){\n            if((i % 4 == 0 &amp;&amp; i % 100 != 0) || i % 400 == 0){\n                ans += 366;\n            }else{\n                ans += 365;\n            }\n        }\n        //复用「1154. 一年中的第几天」中的代码\n        int[] day4month = {31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; month - 1;i++) ans += day4month[i];\n        if(((year % 4 == 0 &amp;&amp; year % 100 != 0) || year % 400 == 0) &amp;&amp; month &gt; 2)ans++;\n        return week[ans % 7];\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220103234250776.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220103234250776.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/cat-and-mouse\" target=\"_blank\">913. 猫和老鼠</a> - 22.01.04</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">这题说实话，题解都看不太明白，CV 完事补个中等题。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/find-first-and-last-position-of-element-in-sorted-array/\" target=\"_blank\">34. 在排序数组中查找元素的第一个和最后一个位置</a></h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int[] searchRange(int[] nums, int target) {\n        int[] ans = {-1,-1};\n        ans[0] = binarySearch(nums,target,true);\n        ans[1] = binarySearch(nums,target,false);\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n    public int binarySearch(int[] nums, int target, boolean isLeft){\n        int left = 0;\n        int right = nums.length - 1;\n        int ans = -1;\n        while(left &lt;= right){\n            int mid = (left + right) / 2;\n            if(nums[mid] &lt; target){\n                left = mid + 1;\n            }else if(nums[mid] &gt; target){\n                right = mid - 1;\n            }else{\n                ans = mid;\n                if(isLeft){\n                    //如果要找的是最左边的，让右区间往左移一位\n                    right = mid - 1;\n                }else{\n                    //如果要找的是最右边的，让左区间往右移一位\n                    left = mid + 1;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220104234351973.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220104234351973.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/replace-all-s-to-avoid-consecutive-repeating-characters/\" target=\"_blank\">1576. 替换所有的问号</a> - 22.01.05</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public String modifyString(String s) {\n        int n = s.length();\n        char[] ss = s.toCharArray();\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; n;i++){\n            if(ss[i] == \'?\'){\n                for(int j = 0;j &lt; 26;j++){\n                    char c = (char)(\'a\' + j);\n                    if((i - 1 &lt; 0 || ss[i - 1] != c) &amp;&amp; (i + 1 &gt;= n || ss[i + 1] != c)){\n                        ss[i] = c;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return String.valueOf(ss);\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220105055648217.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220105055648217.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/simplify-path/\" target=\"_blank\">71. 简化路径</a> - 22.01.06</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public String simplifyPath(String path) {\n        String[] paths = path.split(\"/\");\n        Deque&lt;String&gt; stack = new LinkedList&lt;&gt;();\n        for(String p : paths){\n            if(\".\".equals(p)){\n                continue;\n            }else if(\"..\".equals(p)){\n                if(!stack.isEmpty()){\n                    stack.pollLast();\n                }\n            }else if(!\"\".equals(p)){\n                stack.offerLast(p);\n            }\n        }\n        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();\n        if(stack.isEmpty()){\n            sb.append(\"/\");\n        }\n        while(!stack.isEmpty()){\n            sb.append(\"/\").append(stack.pollFirst());\n        }\n        return sb.toString();\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220106022509379.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220106022509379.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">用双端队列模拟，简化路径时在队列尾部用栈的特性 offer poll，拼接结果时在队列头部 poll。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/maximum-nesting-depth-of-the-parentheses/\" target=\"_blank\">1614. 括号的最大嵌套深度</a> - 22.01.07</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int maxDepth(String s) {\n        //并不需要真的创建一个栈，只需要记录栈的大小即可\n        int size = 0;\n        int ans = 0;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; s.length();i++){\n            char c = s.charAt(i);\n            if(\'(\' == c){\n                size++;\n                ans = Math.max(size,ans);\n            }else if(\')\' == c){\n                size--;\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220107004720917.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220107004720917.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/gray-code/\" target=\"_blank\">89. 格雷编码</a> - 22.01.08</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public List&lt;Integer&gt; grayCode(int n) {\n        List&lt;Integer&gt; ans = new ArrayList&lt;Integer&gt;();\n        for (int i = 0; i &lt; 1 &lt;&lt; n /*Math.pow(2,n)*/; i++) {\n            //格雷码的公式\n            ans.add((i &gt;&gt; 1) ^ i);\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220108003750538.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220108003750538.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">这题太怪了，明明就是一种编码方式，该用公式用就完事了，非要用原始人的方式解题，那么为什么不从二进制的实现做起呢。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/slowest-key/\" target=\"_blank\">1629. 按键持续时间最长的键</a> - 22.01.09</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public char slowestKey(int[] releaseTimes, String keysPressed) {\n        int n = keysPressed.length();\n        char[] chars = keysPressed.toCharArray();\n        //持续时间最长的键的index\n        int maxIndex = 0;\n        //持续时间最长的时间\n        int maxTimes = -1;\n        //上一个键的时间\n        int lastTimes = 0;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; n;i++){\n            int curTimes = releaseTimes[i] - lastTimes;\n            lastTimes = releaseTimes[i];\n            if(maxTimes &lt; curTimes){\n                maxTimes = curTimes;\n                maxIndex = i;\n            }else if(maxTimes == curTimes){\n                maxIndex = chars[i] &gt; chars[maxIndex] ? i : maxIndex;\n            }\n        }\n        return chars[maxIndex];\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220109010027517.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220109010027517.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">很简单的一遍遍历</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/additive-number/\" target=\"_blank\">306. 累加数</a> - 22.01.10</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    int len;\n    char[] nums;\n\n    public boolean isAdditiveNumber(String num) {\n        len = num.length();\n        if(len &lt; 3) return false;\n        nums = num.toCharArray();\n        long num1 = 0;\n        //len / 2: 第一个数如果超过一半的长度，后面的数就已经无法相等了\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; len / 2;i++){\n            num1 = num1 * 10 + nums[i] - \'0\';\n            long num2 = 0;\n            for(int j = i + 1;j &lt; len - 1;j++){\n                num2 = num2 * 10 + nums[j] - \'0\';\n                if(num2 == 0){\n                    if(judge(num1, num2, j + 1)){\n                        return true;\n                    }\n                    //num2 == 0,如果不能一通到底，则在第一轮遍历直接跳出\n                    break;\n                }\n                if(judge(num1, num2, j + 1)){\n                    return true;\n                }\n            }\n            if(num1 == 0){\n                //num1 == 0,如果不能一通到底，则在第一轮遍历直接跳出\n                break;\n            }\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n\n    private boolean judge(long num1, long num2, int num3Index){\n        //累加序列里的数 不会 以 0 开头，但这个数本身可以是0\n        if(nums[num3Index] == \'0\'){\n            if(num1 + num2 == 0){\n                //递归出口\n                if(num3Index == len - 1){\n                    return true;\n                }\n                //进入递归，判断下一个累加序列\n                else if(judge(num2, 0, num3Index + 1)){\n                    return true;\n                }\n            }\n            //因为 累加序列里的数 不会 以 0 开头，所以当这个数是 0 时，第一轮判断不符合就可以跳出了\n            return false;\n        }\n        long num3 = 0;\n        for(int i = num3Index;i &lt; len;i++){\n            num3 = num3 * 10 + nums[i] - \'0\';\n            if(num1 + num2 == num3){\n                //递归出口\n                if(i == len - 1){\n                    return true;\n                }\n                //进入递归\n                if(judge(num2, num3, i + 1)){\n                    return true;\n                }\n            }else if(num1 + num2 &lt; num3){\n                //剪枝\n                return false;\n            }\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220110042310762.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220110042310762.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">今天的题是究极<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>O(n^3)</code></span>遍历。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/escape-a-large-maze/\" target=\"_blank\">1036. 逃离大迷宫</a> - 22.01.11</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    int N = (int)1e6;\n    int[] dx = {0,1,0,-1};\n    int[] dy = {1,0,-1,0};\n    Set&lt;String&gt; blockSet = new HashSet&lt;&gt;();\n\n    public boolean isEscapePossible(int[][] blocked, int[] source, int[] target) { \n        if(blocked.length == 0) return true;\n        for(int[] b : blocked){\n            blockSet.add(b[0] + \",\" + b[1]);\n        }\n        return \n        dfs(source[0], source[1], source[0], source[1], target[0], target[1], new HashSet&lt;&gt;())\n        &amp;&amp;\n        dfs(target[0], target[1], target[0], target[1], source[0], source[1], new HashSet&lt;&gt;());\n    }\n\n    private boolean dfs(int x, int y, int fromX, int fromY, int toX, int toY, Set&lt;String&gt; visitedSet){\n        if(x == toX &amp;&amp; y == toY){\n            return true;\n        }\n        //曼哈顿距离大于200，则肯定能够绕路到达\n        if (Math.abs(fromX - x) + Math.abs(fromY - y) &gt; 200) {\n            return true;\n        }\n        visitedSet.add(x + \",\" + y);\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; 4;i++){\n            int nx = x + dx[i];\n            int ny = y + dy[i];\n            if(judge(nx,ny,visitedSet) &amp;&amp; dfs(nx, ny, fromX, fromY, toX, toY, visitedSet)){\n                return true;\n            }\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n\n    private boolean judge(int x, int y, Set&lt;String&gt; visitedSet){\n        if(x &lt; 0 || y &lt; 0 || x &gt;= N || y &gt;= N) return false;\n        String hash = x + \",\" + y;\n        if(blockSet.contains(hash) || visitedSet.contains(hash)) return false;\n        return true;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220111132025561.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220111132025561.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">不同于普通的 DFS、BFS，因为数据范围太大，如果直接开二维数组来存<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>matrix</code></span>或是<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>visited</code></span>，会超出内存限制，而应该保存对应位置到<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>Set</code></span>中。同样的，为了不超时，应该在搜索一定的范围后剪枝，因为<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>0 &lt;= blocked.length &lt;= 200</code></span>，如果能搜出<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>曼哈顿距离</code></span>大于 200 的范围，则能保证出发点没有被 block 住，一定能到达。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/increasing-triplet-subsequence/\" target=\"_blank\">334. 递增的三元子序列</a> - 22.01.12</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public boolean increasingTriplet(int[] nums) {\n        if(nums.length &lt; 3)return false;\n        int small = Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n        int mid = Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n        for(int n : nums){\n            if(n &lt;= small){\n                small = n;\n            }else if(n &lt;= mid){\n                mid = n;\n            }else{\n                return true;\n            }\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220112201136955.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220112201136955.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">很巧妙的一个方法。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/largest-number-at-least-twice-of-others/\" target=\"_blank\">747. 至少是其他数字两倍的最大数</a> - 22.01.13</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int dominantIndex(int[] nums) {\n        int max = -1;\n        int max2 = -1;\n        int maxIndex = -1;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; nums.length;i++){\n            if(nums[i] &gt; max){\n                maxIndex = i;\n                max2 = max;\n                max = nums[i];\n            }else if(nums[i] &gt; max2){\n                max2 = nums[i];\n            }\n        }\n        return max &gt;= max2 * 2 ? maxIndex : -1;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220113183826381.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220113183826381.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/find-k-pairs-with-smallest-sums/\" target=\"_blank\">373. 查找和最小的 K 对数字</a> - 22.01.14</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public List&lt;List&lt;Integer&gt;&gt; kSmallestPairs(int[] nums1, int[] nums2, int k) {\n        List&lt;List&lt;Integer&gt;&gt; ans = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;(k);\n        PriorityQueue&lt;int[]&gt; heap = new PriorityQueue&lt;&gt;((a,b)-&gt;(nums1[a[0]] + nums2[a[1]]) - (nums1[b[0]] + nums2[b[1]]));\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; Math.min(k,nums1.length);i++){\n            heap.offer(new int[]{i,0});\n        }\n        while(k-- &gt; 0 &amp;&amp; !heap.isEmpty()){\n            int[] cur = heap.poll();\n            ans.add(Arrays.asList(nums1[cur[0]],nums2[cur[1]]));\n            if(++cur[1] &lt; nums2.length){\n                heap.offer(cur);\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220114231624102.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220114231624102.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">想不到的都难，能想到的都不难。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/calculate-money-in-leetcode-bank/\" target=\"_blank\">1716. 计算力扣银行的钱</a> - 22.01.15</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int totalMoney(int n) {\n        int week = n / 7;\n        int mod = n % 7;\n        return 28 * week + 7 * week * (week - 1) / 2 + (week + 1) * mod + mod * (mod - 1) / 2;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220115235520800.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220115235520800.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">简单题我重拳出击。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/linked-list-random-node/\" target=\"_blank\">382. 链表随机节点</a> - 22.01.16</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    List&lt;Integer&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\n    Random random = new Random();\n    public Solution(ListNode head) {\n        while(head != null){\n            list.add(head.val);\n            head = head.next;\n        }\n    }\n    \n    public int getRandom() {\n        return list.get(random.nextInt(list.size()));\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220116121702610.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220116121702610.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">蓄水池抽样听起来好熟悉，似乎在概率论学过？但一看数学推导...我还是用 O(n) 吧...</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/count-vowels-permutation/\" target=\"_blank\">1220. 统计元音字母序列的数目</a> - 22.01.17</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    /*\n    0. a &lt;- e i u\n    1. e &lt;- a i\n    2. i &lt;- e o\n    3. o &lt;- i\n    4. u &lt;- i o\n    */\n    long mod = (int)1e9 + 7;\n\n    public int countVowelPermutation(int n) {\n        long[] state = new long[5];\n        Arrays.fill(state, 1);\n        for(int i = 1;i &lt; n;i++){\n            state = fsm(state);\n        }\n        int ans = 0;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; 5;i++){\n            ans += state[i];\n            ans %= mod;\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n    private long[] fsm(long[] s){\n        long[] ss = new long[5];\n        ss[0] = (s[1] + s[2] + s[4]) % mod;\n        ss[1] = (s[0] + s[2]) % mod;\n        ss[2] = (s[1] + s[3]) % mod;\n        ss[3] = (s[2]) % mod;\n        ss[4] = (s[2] + s[3]) % mod;\n        return ss;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220117200719997.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220117200719997.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">尝试使用状态机来做。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/minimum-time-difference/\" target=\"_blank\">539. 最小时间差</a> - 22.01.18</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int findMinDifference(List&lt;String&gt; timePoints) {\n        if(timePoints.size() &gt;= 1440) return 0;\n        int[] n = new int[1440 * 2];\n        for(String t:timePoints){\n            int m = string2int(t);\n            n[m]++;\n            n[m + 1440]++;\n            if(n[m] &gt; 1)return 0;\n        }\n        int ans = 1440;\n        int last = -1;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt;= 1440 * 1.5;i++){\n            if(n[i] == 0)continue;\n            if(last != -1) ans = Math.min(ans,i - last);\n            last = i;\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n    private int string2int(String time){\n        return (time.charAt(0) - \'0\') * 10 * 60 +\n               (time.charAt(1) - \'0\') * 60      +\n               (time.charAt(3) - \'0\') * 10      +\n               (time.charAt(4) - \'0\');\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220118235943098.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220118235943098.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/contains-duplicate-ii/\" target=\"_blank\">219. 存在重复元素 II</a> - 22.01.19</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public boolean containsNearbyDuplicate(int[] nums, int k) {\n        Map&lt;Integer,Integer&gt; map = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; nums.length;i++){\n            if(map.get(nums[i]) != null &amp;&amp; Math.abs(map.get(nums[i]) - i) &lt;= k){\n                return true;\n            }\n            map.put(nums[i],i);\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220119002551003.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220119002551003.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">竟然是两年前用 cpp 写过的题</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/stone-game-ix/\" target=\"_blank\">2029. 石子游戏 IX</a> - 22.01.20</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alice 和 Bob 的脑瘫游戏我是没有一丁点兴趣参与。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/the-kth-factor-of-n/\" target=\"_blank\">1492. n 的第 k 个因子</a></h2><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int kthFactor(int n, int k) {\n        int cnt = 0;\n        for(int i = 1;i &lt;= n;i++){\n            if(n % i == 0){\n                cnt++;\n                if(cnt == k) return i;\n            }\n        }\n        return -1;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220120205414163.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220120205414163.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">这题竟然也算中等题。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/jump-game-iv/\" target=\"_blank\">1345. 跳跃游戏 IV</a> - 22.01.21</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int minJumps(int[] arr) {\n        int n = arr.length;\n        //构建一个arr[i]可以「等值跳」的map，可以跳的下标可能有多个，so value=List\n        Map&lt;Integer,List&lt;Integer&gt;&gt; map = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n        //从后往前添加，让后面的优先跳\n        for(int i = n - 1;i &gt;= 0;i--){\n            List&lt;Integer&gt; list = map.getOrDefault(arr[i],new ArrayList&lt;&gt;());\n            list.add(i);\n            map.put(arr[i],list);\n        }\n        int[] dist = new int[n];\n        Arrays.fill(dist, -1);\n        Queue&lt;Integer&gt; q = new ArrayDeque&lt;&gt;();\n        q.offer(0);\n        dist[0] = 0;\n        while(!q.isEmpty()){\n            int cur = q.poll();\n            int step = dist[cur];\n            if(cur == n - 1) return step;\n            if(cur + 1 &lt; n &amp;&amp; dist[cur + 1] == -1){\n                q.offer(cur + 1);\n                dist[cur + 1] = step + 1;\n            }\n            if(cur - 1 &gt;= 0 &amp;&amp; dist[cur - 1] == -1){\n                q.offer(cur - 1);\n                dist[cur - 1] = step + 1;\n            }\n            List&lt;Integer&gt; list = map.get(arr[cur]);\n            if(list != null){\n                for(Integer i : list){\n                    if(dist[i] == -1){\n                        q.offer(i);\n                        dist[i] = step + 1;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n            map.remove(arr[cur]);\n        }\n        return 0;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220121205452164.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220121205452164.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">挺有意思的一道题。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/remove-palindromic-subsequences/\" target=\"_blank\">1332. 删除回文子序列</a> - 22.01.22</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int removePalindromeSub(String s) {\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; s.length() / 2;i++){\n            if(s.charAt(i) != s.charAt(s.length() - 1 - i)){\n                //不是回文串，删两次\n                return 2;\n            }\n        }\n        return 1;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220122194631765.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220122194631765.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">其实是道考察眼力的题，题目要求中不是「子串」，而是「子序列」，所以可以跳着删。如果原串不是回文串，答案就是 2，第一次把<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>a</code></span>全删了，第二次把<span style=\"color: rgb(228, 48, 94); background-color: rgb(253, 242, 245);\"><code>b</code></span>全删了，如果是回文串，答案就是 1。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/stock-price-fluctuation/\" target=\"_blank\">2034. 股票价格波动</a> - 22.01.23</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class StockPrice {\n    int curTime;\n    //{时间戳:价格}\n    Map&lt;Integer,Integer&gt; map;\n    //treeMap{价格:该价格出现的次数}\n    //利用TreeMap有序特性，首尾Key便是最低最高价格\n    TreeMap&lt;Integer,Integer&gt; treeMap;\n\n    public StockPrice() {\n        curTime = 0;\n        map = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n        treeMap = new TreeMap&lt;&gt;();\n    }\n    \n    public void update(int timestamp, int price) {\n        curTime = Math.max(curTime,timestamp);\n        if(map.containsKey(timestamp)){\n            //存在该时间戳，维护treeMap\n            //旧价格\n            int old = map.get(timestamp);\n            int cnt = treeMap.get(old);\n            if(cnt == 1){\n                treeMap.remove(old);\n            }else{\n                treeMap.put(old,cnt - 1);\n            }\n        }\n        map.put(timestamp,price);\n        treeMap.put(price,treeMap.getOrDefault(price,0) + 1);\n    }\n    \n    public int current() {\n        return map.get(curTime);\n    }\n    \n    public int maximum() {\n        return treeMap.lastKey();\n    }\n    \n    public int minimum() {\n        return treeMap.firstKey();\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220123235739437.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220123235739437.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/second-minimum-time-to-reach-destination/\" target=\"_blank\">2045. 到达目的地的第二短时间</a> - 22.01.24</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">寄了。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/count-of-matches-in-tournament/\" target=\"_blank\">1688. 比赛中的配对次数</a> - 22.01.25</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int numberOfMatches(int n) {\n        return n - 1;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/detect-squares/\" target=\"_blank\">2013. 检测正方形</a> - 22.01.26</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class DetectSquares {\n    Map&lt;Integer, Map&lt;Integer, Integer&gt;&gt; row2Col = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();\n    \n    public void add(int[] point) {\n        int x = point[0], y = point[1];\n        Map&lt;Integer, Integer&gt; col2Cnt = row2Col.getOrDefault(x, new HashMap&lt;&gt;());\n        col2Cnt.put(y, col2Cnt.getOrDefault(y, 0) + 1);\n        row2Col.put(x, col2Cnt);\n    }\n    \n    public int count(int[] point) {\n        int x = point[0], y = point[1];\n        int ans = 0;\n        Map&lt;Integer, Integer&gt; col2Cnt = row2Col.getOrDefault(x, new HashMap&lt;&gt;());\n        for (int ny : col2Cnt.keySet()) {\n            if (ny == y) continue;\n            int c1 = col2Cnt.get(ny);\n            int len = y - ny;\n            int[] nums = new int[]{x + len, x - len};\n            for (int nx : nums) {\n                Map&lt;Integer, Integer&gt; temp = row2Col.getOrDefault(nx, new HashMap&lt;&gt;());\n                int c2 = temp.getOrDefault(y, 0), c3 = temp.getOrDefault(ny, 0);\n                ans += c1 * c2 * c3;\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">快写完了代码飞了，直接 copy 题解。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/number-of-valid-words-in-a-sentence/\" target=\"_blank\">2047. 句子中的有效单词数</a> - 22.01.27</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int countValidWords(String sentence) {\n        int ans = 0;\n        String[] split = sentence.split(\" \");\n        for(String s : split){\n            if(judge(s))ans++;\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n\n    private boolean judge(String s){\n        if(s.length() == 0)return false;\n        if((s.charAt(0) == \'!\' || s.charAt(0) == \'.\' || s.charAt(0) == \',\') &amp;&amp; s.length() == 1)return true;\n        if(s.charAt(0) &lt; \'a\' || s.charAt(0) &gt; \'z\')return false;\n        int cnt = 0;\n        for(int i = 0;i &lt; s.length();i++){\n            char a = s.charAt(i);\n            if(a &gt;= \'0\' &amp;&amp; a &lt;= \'9\')return false;\n            if(a == \'-\'){\n                cnt++;\n                if(cnt &gt; 1)return false;\n                if(i == s.length() - 1)return false;\n                if(s.charAt(i + 1) &lt; \'a\' || s.charAt(i + 1) &gt; \'z\')return false;\n            }\n            if((a == \'!\' || a == \'.\' || a == \',\') &amp;&amp; i != s.length() - 1)return false;\n        }\n        return true;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220127051300093.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220127051300093.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">瞎勾八写就完事了。</p><h2><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/the-number-of-weak-characters-in-the-game/\" target=\"_blank\">1996. 游戏中弱角色的数量</a> - 22.01.28</h2><p><br></p><pre style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><code class=\"language-java\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\">class Solution {\n    public int numberOfWeakCharacters(int[][] properties) {\n        Arrays.sort(properties,(a,b)-&gt;{\n            return a[0] != b[0] ? b[0] - a[0] : a[1] - b[1];\n        });\n        int ans = 0;\n        int max = 0;\n        for(int[] p : properties){\n            if(p[1] &lt; max){\n                ans++;\n            }else{\n                max = p[1];\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}\n\n<span>Copy</span></code></pre><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.naccl.top/blog/blogHosting/2021/12/B02/image-20220128095249525.png#w70\" alt=\"image-20220128095249525.png\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 546.344px;\"></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">作者：Naccl <a href=\"https://naccl.top/about\" target=\"\">（联系作者）</a></li></ul>', '0', '1362', '1', '2024-01-15 19:37:19', '2024-01-15 19:37:19');

